&lt;h1 style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 20px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h1 style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 20px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h1 style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 20px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Category-defining tech. Career-defining work.&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Lots of tech companies disrupt. But, many fail when they try to scale. We&#39;re different. CockroachDB makes it easier for companies to build and scale apps. This is how and why we&#39;re helping some of the most innovative companies on the planet. We tackle problems head-on and focus on solutions that create lasting impact.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Because when our customers win, we all win.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
