&lt;h2&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Cockroach Labs, recruiters are talent advisors, embedded partners to the business who shape hiring strategy, influence decisions, and raise the bar on how we scale our teams. We&#39;re looking for a Recruiter to own the end-to-end process for mid-level roles across the GTM organization. You&#39;ll run structured processes, close strong candidates in a competitive market, and be a genuine strategic partner to your hiring managers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;To be eligible, you must be based in Austin, TX.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will begin as a contract position with the potential to convert to full-time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own full-cycle searches across mid-level GTM roles, from intake through close&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build consultative partnerships with hiring managers — set expectations, share market data, and push back when needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Source proactively beyond inbound across LinkedIn, referrals, talent mapping, and community channels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and run structured, competency-based interview processes and keep debriefs moving toward decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hold a high bar on candidate experience at every stage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring AI tools into your workflow where they create real leverage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What We&#39;re Looking For&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2–4 years of full-cycle recruiting experience in B2B SaaS or enterprise tech&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record hiring GTM roles in a competitive market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong proactive sourcing skills, especially for high-velocity pipelines&lt;/li&gt;
