&lt;p&gt;As an Incident Manager at Cockroach Labs, you will lead the coordination and resolution of incidents across internal systems, CockroachDB Cloud, customer-hosted environments, and security/compliance events in the NA region. You will drive structured response efforts, partner with cross-functional teams to identify root causes, and help prevent recurrence in an environment where the pace is fast and the bar is high.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To be eligible for this role, you must be located in the Pacific time zone.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
