&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Cockroach Labs exists to build what comes next — before the world requires it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;We created CockroachDB to survive failures, scale without compromise, and adapt to changing conditions automatically. Now we’re helping define a future where complexity fades into the background and infrastructure simply works, no matter the scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;This is the kind of challenge that attracts people who want to shape industries, not just participate in them. The work is ambitious, the standards are high, and the impact is real.&lt;/p&gt;
